description:
This is a 32 minute workout called '30 min Yoga for Weight Loss | Fat Burning Workout | At - Home' from the channel Akshaya Agnes.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Yoga.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Meditative Grind vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate.
